== 紀念 ==
2017年4月26日，[[Google|Google]]首頁展示了以卡西尼-惠更斯号为主题的[[Google涂鸦|Google涂鸦]]，以紀念卡西尼号探测器穿越土星与土星环内缘。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com/doodles/cassini-spacecraft-dives-between-saturn-and-its-rings?hl=zh-CN |title=Google涂鸦：卡西尼号太空船在土星与土星环之间飞掠！ |access-date=2017-04-26 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202025752/https://www.google.com/doodles/cassini-spacecraft-dives-between-saturn-and-its-rings?hl=zh-CN |dead-url=no }}</ref>

